    "name": "Elite Dangerous",
    "steam_appid": 359320,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/c7e6cb394bc08e8fca6484d37c0d64c1.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=775 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索传奇《Elite》系列的下个篇章。《Elite Dangerous》是宏伟的大型多人太空史诗世界，借由无缝连系的星系，玩家会塑造循序渐进的叙事方式，以及写实比例再现的全银河系，将 1984 年游戏界的元祖开放世界冒险带到现代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这广阔的背景下，驾驶自己的星舰航向星空，尽一切努力在不断变化的未来银河沙盒中生存下来。获得财富和权力、发展您的技能和知识，并努力在精英强权之列中脱颖而出。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个银河系强权林立、星际战争如火如荼的时代，您的故事会影响彼此紧密连结的体验，以及精心打造的循序渐进原创故事。无论是发现新世界，还是进行热血的太空战斗，以及慎密重现的贸易经济，银河系正等着您来探索。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/ed3195febcc65b7c3c4706452b416f27.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/ed3195febcc65b7c3c4706452b416f27.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/ed3195febcc65b7c3c4706452b416f27.mp4?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>奇景银河 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >银河系的 4 千亿个星系是《Elite Dangerous》开放式玩法广阔而动态的舞台。用真实的天文数据构建，我们星系中的所有恒星、行星、卫星、小行星带与黑洞皆以真实的银河系比例再现。规划一条穿越其他指挥官从未前往过的星系路线，并利用地面探勘车辆探索陌生世界的表面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/9ffedd76aee495e316a1bafc77a3a3cb.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/9ffedd76aee495e316a1bafc77a3a3cb.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/9ffedd76aee495e316a1bafc77a3a3cb.mp4?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>找到您的完美船舰 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 35 种不同的宇宙飞船可供您指挥，从轻型探索船舰到适合用来战斗的巨型太空船统统都有。建造各式各样的船舰并依您的游玩风格进行改装。自定义每一项组件、武器和可选模块，以强化提升您船舰的能力。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/218af54a80a76ee829c34ef72409719c.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/218af54a80a76ee829c34ef72409719c.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/218af54a80a76ee829c34ef72409719c.mp4?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>点亮自己的航迹  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在银河系中猎杀、探索、战斗、挖矿、走私和贸易。独自一人或与最多三位朋友一起在分队开辟出自己的路。加入一支志同道合的指挥官中队，一同分享星际冒险过程中的高低起伏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有了星系殖民机制，夺取和扩展您自己星系的权力就掌握在您手中。无论是创造蓬勃发展的新经济、繁忙的贸易中心，还是新的运输航站，银河系等着您来实现理想。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/74692a0a9a99cd02a42540fb4b75de7d.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/74692a0a9a99cd02a42540fb4b75de7d.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>独特的连通游戏体验 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Elite Dangerous》的浩瀚银河围绕着玩家的行动展开。在这个银河系强权林立、星际战争如火如荼的时代，每个玩家的个人经历都会影响太空模拟和精心打造的循序渐进原创故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他指挥官合作完成关键的社区目标活动，能永久改变银河系的状态，您也会因为在过程中的贡献而获得独家奖励和认可。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与银河系的超级强权结盟，利用权力游戏改变星际景观。通过各种方式巩固您自己星系的权力或削弱对手，包括入侵星际航站广告和攻击巨型要塞母舰。每一个贡献都很重要。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/a4b49e4ff65a8fe4230051b046041e96.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/a4b49e4ff65a8fe4230051b046041e96.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/a4b49e4ff65a8fe4230051b046041e96.mp4?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>大型多人在线 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在广阔的超巨大多人游戏世界体验中，与其他玩家不期而遇。既可以在单人模式中独自体验相互连通的星系，也可以在开放游玩中与世界各地的玩家一起冒险，在那里，你面对的每个驾驶员都可以成为值得信赖的盟友或最致命的敌人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/f4ff5f68696bbc26267e6ebb4947ff13.poster.avif?t=1759842966\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/f4ff5f68696bbc26267e6ebb4947ff13.webm?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/359320/extras/f4ff5f68696bbc26267e6ebb4947ff13.mp4?t=1759842966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>生机勃勃的游戏 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Elite Dangerous》宇宙会不断发展并扩展新的功能和内容。定期的重大更新提供新的机会和玩法，让玩家能探索并改变自己的游玩方式。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
